Uni Scraper

Goal:
---
Build "universal" (cover 85 to 95 % cases) web content scraper.
It should be able performing complex requests, parse pages of different
formats and make extraction storing results where specified.

Solution:
---
Create a frame work which can solve most of the general cases "out-of-the-box"
and can be configured/extended (using 'instances') for specific needs.